<Game>
	<Name>Air Rescue (Europe)</Name>
	<plot>Air Rescue is similar to Choplifter!. You are a driver of a helicopter and the object is to rescue hostages without being shot down by soldiers, jeeps, tanks, choppers, and ground-based missiles, and bring them back to base. A maximum of four hostages can fit into the helicopter at any given time, so it is necessary to make more than one trip. You can choose from a variety of weapons that you can use to shoot down enemies. There are five rounds, which take you through theme parks, burning skyscrapers, army bases, sunken submarines, and caverns. The round ends when you have taken the required number of hostages to the bases.Cheat: Enter Text ModeBefore you switch the machine on, hold in buttons 1 and 2, as well as the Power button. When the introduction begins, rotate the D-Pad clockwise. You should hear a confirmation sound. Release the buttons and then press button 1 to enter Text Mode.</plot>
